## Implementation in Both Screens

Make sure this fixed DatePickerDialog is used in both SignUpScreen and CompleteProfileScreen by replacing the existing implementations.

You can use any of the three approaches above, but the third one (direct input fields) is probably the most reliable across different Android versions and devices. Choose the one that works best for your app's requirements.

The Material3 DatePicker is the most modern and provides the best user experience, but it requires Material3 and might not be available on all versions of Android.

