I'll enhance the phone sign-in screen with a proper country code dropdown menu that uses a phone number library. Here's the implementation:

```kotlin:app/src/main/java/android/saswat/brewnet/ui/signInandSignUp/Sign In.kt
package android.saswat.brewnet.ui.signInandSignUp

import android.app.Activity
import android.saswat.brewnet.R
import android.saswat.state.AuthState
import android.saswat.state.PhoneAuthState
import android.saswat.viewModel.AuthViewModel
import android.saswat.viewModel.PhoneAuthViewModel
import android.saswat.viewModel.PhoneAuthViewModelFactory
import androidx.activity.compose.rememberLauncherForActivityResult
import androidx.activity.result.contract.ActivityResultContracts
import androidx.compose.foundation.Image
import androidx.compose.foundation.background
import androidx.compose.foundation.border
import androidx.compose.foundation.clickable
